experience.description:
Recruitment for Technical Support, IT and R&D using LinkedIn, and other internet recruiting techniques (EMEA).

Full-cycle recruiting process:
- working with Hiring Managers in order to understand their needs, develop candidate profiles and design the recruitment strategy;
- managing the recruitment process from sourcing (using job boards, professional networking sites, internal database, etc) to initial candidate contact;
- candidate screening;
- competency-based interviewing (in English);
- candidate assessment;
- supporting the onboarding of employees.
